Running Rabbitmq
================

Install
-------

http://docs.celeryproject.org/en/latest/getting-started/broker-installation.html

Run
---

rabbitmq-server
(you don't need to sudo if you used brew)

Running Celery Worker
=====================

./manage.py celery worker --loglevel=info

Runserver
=========

Since the virtualenv defaults to CELERY_ALWAYS_EAGER = False, you may need to
`unset CELERY_ALWAYS_EAGER`
